Capital Markets

Company Overview of Beacon Hill Financial Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Beacon Hill Financial Corp. provides advisory services to limited partners, venture capital, and leveraged buyout funds. Representative clients of this firm are Advent International Corp.; Forstmann Little & Co.; Joseph Littlejohn & Levy; Medical Science Partners; Nash Sells & Partners; Parthenon Capital Inc.; Rhone Capital Partners; and TDG Capital Group Inc. Beacon Hill Financial Corp. is based in Boston, Massachusetts.


120 Water StreetBoston, MA 02109United StatesFounded in 1982



Phone: 617-973-6900

Fax: 617-973-9888

www.beaconhillfinancial.com







Key Executives for Beacon Hill Financial Corp.




Mr. Robert F. Johnston


      	President
      








Ms. Nancy Bonoli


      	Controller
      





Compensation as of Fiscal Year 2017. 

Beacon Hill Financial Corp. Key Developments

Beacon Hill Financial Launches Financial Division; Appoints Todd Games as Division Head
Oct 26 16
Beacon Hill Staffing Group opened its 44th location this month, laying down roots in Bellevue, Washington. The new office opens with Beacon Hill Financial, Beacon Hill's financial staffing division. It is the second division established in the state of Washington, joining nearby Seattle. With these newest additions, Beacon Hill Financial is now present in 13 locations across the country Boston, Chicago, Dallas, Denver, Nashville, New York City, Philadelphia, Washington, D.C. Metro Area, Charlotte, St. Louis, Seattle, Milwaukee and now Bellevue.

Leading the company in the Bellevue marketplace is Todd Games. With extensive experience in the accounting and finance staffing industry, he is regarded for his ability to deliver top-quality talent and customer service to his clients. Priding himself on delivering a flexible 'client first model,' he has provided client solutions that range from entry level to CFO. Prior to joining the company, Mr. Games was a branch manager and top producer for a global accounting and finance staffing firm where he received multiple awards and recognitions.


